"(deletion enabled).\n"
"\n"
"Its priming can no longer be used as-is: a mirror mapping must reconcile the "
"destination before real-time can handle its deletions. Saving will therefore "
"RESET this mapping's primed state — it becomes unavailable for real-time "
"until you prime it again (in mirror mode).\n"
"\n"
"Tip: it is best to decide a mapping's vocation before it holds a lot of "
"data, so this re-priming stays quick.\n"
"\n"
"Save and reset the primed state?"
msgstr ""
"Esta asignación se inicializó como ADITIVA y la está cambiando a ESPEJO "
"(eliminación activada).\n"
"\n"
